      "date": "2014-04-29 18:06:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nDespite being marked as +1 by Maloo (which fooled us into thinking the patch could be landed), this patch failed its own test in all three runs:\n\n Can't open file /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/acl/4924.test:\n  No such file or directory at /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/acl/run line 42.\n sanity test_103: @@@@@@ FAIL: LU-4924 test failed\n\nI expect this file is missing from lustre/tests/Makefile.am file.\n\n  nobase_noinst_DATA += acl/misc.test acl/permissions.test acl/setfacl.test\n -nobase_noinst_DATA += acl/974.test acl/974_remote.test acl/2561.test acl/2561_zfs.test\n +nobase_noinst_DATA += acl/974.test acl/974_remote.test acl/2561.test\n +nobase_noinst_DATA += acl/2561_zfs.test acl/4924.test\n\nThis patch needs to be resubmitted with this fix.",
